Value: Gas2Grid Limited, together with subsidiaries, operates as the petroleum exploration company in Australia, the Philippines, and France. It holds a 100% interest in the Service Contract 44 covering an area of approximately 750 square kilometers located on Cebu Island, the Philippines; and St Griede license located in onshore Aquitaine Basin, France. Gas2Grid Limited was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Sydney, Australia.
